110
00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:17.870
休息時在自己的房間里呢
What if I wear it in my room, during my free time?


111
00:10:19.580 --> 00:10:21.910
如果你一定堅持的話
Well, if you absolutely insist.


112
00:10:24.750 --> 00:10:25.670
我堅持
I do.


113
00:10:27.670 --> 00:10:29.250
她會惹麻煩
She's gona get so much trouble.


114
00:10:34.960 --> 00:10:36.170
先生
Monsieur.


115
00:10:36.800 --> 00:10:39.020
-我吃  -我吃
-je mange  -je mange


116
00:10:39.020 --> 00:10:41.570
-你吃  -你吃
-tu manges  -tu manges


117
00:10:45.520 --> 00:10:47.060
這里真不錯
This is splendid.


118
00:10:47.860 --> 00:10:49.020
這是我們最大的套房
It's our largest suite.


119
00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:53.190
感謝你所做的一切  米切思小姐
Thank you for all the care you've taken, Miss Minchin.


120
00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:56.110
希望我走后莎拉在這里能像在家一樣
