你的玩具和衣服都在這里
And with all your toys and clothes moved in...


128
00:11:42.410 --> 00:11:44.500
就像在家里
...it's as if you were really...


129
00:11:47.750 --> 00:11:49.750
我看見了一樣東西
I think I saw something...


130
00:11:50.420 --> 00:11:52.420
就在那里
...on that chair over there.


131
00:11:56.670 --> 00:12:00.180
