quick as lightning.


173
00:15:28.300 --> 00:15:30.050
天哪  真夠快的
Gosh, she's fast.


174
00:15:42.820 --> 00:15:43.730
媽媽
Mama.


175
00:15:45.820 --> 00:15:46.900
莎拉
Sara?


176
00:15:47.240 --> 00:15:50.070
不能因為一個人耽誤大家的早餐
We are not customed to delay everyone's breakfast for one student.


177
00:15:50.320 --> 00:15:51.740
對不起  可我
I'm sorry, Miss Minchin, but I found my mama...


178
00:15:51.910 --> 00:15:55.250
記住  你不是這里唯一的孩子
You're not the only child here, Sara, you have to remember that.


179
00:16:00.250 --> 00:16:02.590
早安
Yes, yes, yes, good morning.


180
00:16:02.750 --> 00:16:06.340
記得昨天來的那位小姐嗎
I trust you remember our newest pupil from our visit to class yesterday.


181
00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:08.510
莎拉  這位是杜弗吉先生
Sara, this is Monsieur Dufarge.


182
00:16:08.760 --> 00:16:11.010
今天下午你向他學習法語
You willl begin French lessons with him this afternoon.


183
00:16:11.180 --> 00:16:13.010
我非得學嗎
Do I have to?


184
00:16:13.350 --> 00:16:15.270
你當然非學不可
Sara, you most certainly do.


185
00:16:15.520 --> 00:16:18.440
為你的失禮向杜弗吉先生道歉
Now apologize to Monsieur this instance for your rudeness.


186
00:16:18.690 --> 00:16:21.360
-對不起  我不是想冒犯他  -道歉
-But I didn't mean to be rude.  -Now!


187
00:16:37.710 --> 00:16:42.880
這孩子不需要再學法語了  她說得很好
This child doesn't need to learn French. She practically is French!


188
00:16:43.040 --> 00:16:44.460
她的法語很好  跟他爸爸學的
She learned from her father.


189
00:16:44.710 --> 00:16:46.880
我非常清楚她說什么
I understood perfectly well what she said, Monsieur.


190
00:16:47.130 --> 00:16:49.300
我們想告訴您的
I'm sorry.  But we tried to tell you.


191
00:16:49.470 --> 00:16:52.050
她可以去教小一點的孩子
Well, perhaps She can tutor the younger children...


192
00:16:52.300 --> 00:16:56.720
或許她還能幫您糾正發音
...and just be able to help you with your pronunciation, Miss Minchin.


193
00:16:57.140 --> 00:17:00.310
我聞到的是香腸味嗎
Are those sausages I smell?


194
00:17:14.740 --> 00:17:16.080
謝謝
Thank you.


195
00:17:16.080 --> 00:17:19.160
餐桌上不許講話
Sara, there's no talking at the table.


196
00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:21.670
這不正常
Doesn't seem natural.


197
00:17:24.750 --> 00:17:26.500
我不想再重復
I won't say it again.


198
00:17:35.430 --> 00:17:37.350
7乘以5是35
Seven times five is 35.


199
00:17:38.350 --> 00:17:40.520
7乘以6是42
Seven times six is 42.


200
00:17:40.770 --> 00:17:42.520
7乘以7是49
Seven times seven is 49.


201
00:17:43.100 --> 00:17:45.440
7乘以8是
Seven times eight is...


202
00:17:45.690 --> 00:17:47.110
58
...58.


203
00:17:48.280 --> 00:17:50.700
不  等等  54
No, wait. 54?


