00:17:54.370 --> 00:17:57.120
72  93  還是12
Or 72? Or 93? Or 12?


206
00:17:57.870 --> 00:17:59.700
對不起  米切思小姐
I'm sorry, Miss Minchin.


207
00:18:00.200 --> 00:18:02.710
昨晚我背了幾個小時
I studied for hours last night.


208
00:18:02.960 --> 00:18:04.960
我簡直不敢相信
I find that very hard to believe.


209
00:18:05.170 --> 00:18:07.500
我想你父親應該知道這些
And I imagine your father will as well.


210
00:18:07.880 --> 00:18:09.960
求你別告訴他
Please don't tell him, Miss Minchin.


211
00:18:10.510 --> 00:18:12.220
我保證下次會做對
I promise I'll do better.


212
00:18:12.590 --> 00:18:14.180
求你了
Please.


213
00:18:14.390 --> 00:18:15.890
拉維妮亞  你來算
Lavinia, you may continue.


214
00:18:16.890 --> 00:18:19.560
7乘以8是56
Seven times eight is 56.


215
00:18:20.180 --> 00:18:21.810
7乘以9
Seven times nine...


216
00:18:22.060 --> 00:18:24.060
是63
...is 63.


217
00:18:33.900 --> 00:18:35.240
親愛的爸爸
Dear Papa:


218
00:18:35.530 --> 00:18:37.160
我已經開始想你了
I miss you already.


219
00:18:38.080 --> 00:18:39.200
這里一切都好
Things are fine.


220
00:18:39.410 --> 00:18:43.500
只是我沒想到學校有這么多規矩
Except I never imagined there would be so many rules at school.


221
00:18:43.750 --> 00:18:46.080
我想它們存在一定有道理
I guess they're there for a purpose...


222
00:18:46.380 --> 00:18:48.590
我正努力去遵守
...and I'm trying hard to obey them.


223
00:18:48.840 --> 00:18:51.840
但我還是覺得我做錯了什么
But I get the feeling I'm doing something wrong.


224
00:19:09.360 --> 00:19:10.860
再見  爸爸
Goodbye, Father.


225
00:19:12.940 --> 00:19:13.990
再見  我的孩子
Bye, son.


226
00:19:29.460 --> 00:19:30.880
希望你讀這封信的時候
I hope when you read this...


227
00:19:31.130 --> 00:19:35.050
臉上帶著微笑  心里充滿快樂
...it kindles your heart and puts a smile on your face.


228
00:19:35.300 --> 00:19:39.800
我真的為你驕傲  每時每刻都在思念著你
Papa, I'm so proud of you. And I think about you every moment.


229
00:19:40.050 --> 00:19:42.140
永遠永遠愛你
And I love you forever.


230
00:19:42.810 --> 00:19:44.480
你的莎拉
Your Sara.


231
00:19:57.240 --> 00:19:59.660
洛蒂  再別鬧了
Lottie, you mustn't get so excited.


232
00:19:59.870 --> 00:20:01.490
洛蒂  親愛的
Lottie? Precious?


233
00:20:01.740 --> 00:20:05.830
求你了  洛蒂寶貝  別再叫了
Oh, please, Lottie dear! Please stop screaming!


234
00:20:06.080 --> 00:20:10.080
想不想吃餅干  要吃嗎
How about a cookie? Would you like that?


235
00:20:10.710 --> 00:20:12.170
我去給你拿
I'll get a cookie.


236
00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:23.680
你這樣鬧別人都沒法學習了
It's very hard to study with you carrying on like this.


237
00:20:23.930 --> 00:20:25.020
我要媽媽
I want my mama!


238
00:20:25.430 --> 00:20:26.600
你很快就會見到她
You'll see her soon.


239
00:20:26.850 --> 00:20:31.560
不會  她死了  我再見不到她了
No, I won't. She's dead, and I won't ever see her again!


240
00:20:31.860 --> 00:20:34.030
我也沒有媽媽
Well, I don't have a mother either.


241
00:20:38.110 --> 00:20:39.490
是嗎
You don't?


242
00:20:41.030 --> 00:20:42.280
她在哪
Where is she?


243
00:20:42.620 --> 00:20:45.370
在天堂  和我小妹妹在一起
In heaven with my baby sister.


244
00:20:46.290 --> 00:20:48.290
這不意味著我不能和她說話
That doesn't mean I can't talk to her.


245
00:20:48.500 --> 00:20:52.130
我什么都跟她說  我知道她聽得見
I tell her everything, I know she hears me.


246
00:20:52.380 --> 00:20:53.790
怎么會
How?


247
00:20:54.750 --> 00:20:56.710
因為天使都能聽見
Because that's what angels do.


248
00:20:56.960 --> 00:20:59.880
-你媽媽是天使  -當然
-Your mama's an angel?  -Of course.


249
00:21:00.130 --> 00:21:04.060
你的媽媽也是 有美麗的絲翅膀
And so is yours. With beautiful wings of silk...


250
00:21:04.310 --> 00:21:06.350
戴著玫瑰花冠
...and a crown of baby rosebuds.


251
00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:09.310
她們都住在城堡里
And they all live together in a castle.


252
00:21:09.480 --> 00:21:11.650
知道城堡是什么造的嗎
Do you know what it's made of?


253
00:21:11.980 --> 00:21:13.270
是向日葵
Sunflowers...


254
00:21:13.520 --> 00:21:18.070
幾千朵向日葵像黃金一般閃著光芒
...hundreds of them, so bright they shine like gold.


255
00:21:18.740 --> 00:21:21.410
天使們想去什么地方
When the angels want to go someplace...


256
00:21:21.610 --> 00:21:24.160
就吹口哨  像這樣
...they just whistle, like this.


257
00:21:31.080 --> 00:21:35.170
云彩飛到城堡大門帶上她們
And a cloud floats to the castle and picks them up.


258
00:21:35.340 --> 00:21:37.760
天使飛向天空
As the angels fly through the sky...


259
00:21:38.670 --> 00:21:41.260
就像坐著魔毯
...riding the cloud like a magic carpet...


260
00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:44.510
在月光下穿梭于星星之問
...under the moon and through the stars...


261
00:21:48.770 --> 00:21:51.440
直至飛到我們頭頂上
...until they're hovering right above us.


262
00:21:54.310 --> 00:21:58.030
她們在天上注視著我們是否快樂
That's how they can look down and see if we're all right.


263
00:21:59.860 --> 00:22:02.780
有時她們會給我們捎話
And sometimes they even send messages to us.


264
00:22:05.780 --> 00:22:08.190
你這樣又哭又鬧
Of course, you can't hear the messages


265
00:22:08.190 --> 00:22:10.870
就聽不見她們說什么了
if you're kicking and screaming as loudly as you were.


266
00:22:12.620 --> 00:22:16.880
不過她們會再說好幾遍  怕我們沒聽見
But they always try again, just in case we've missed it.


267
00:22:19.960 --> 00:22:20.970
等等
Hey, wait!


268
00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:25.640
那是貝琪  她不能跟我們講話
That's Becky. She's not allowed to talk to us.


269
00:22:25.800 --> 00:22:27.010
為什么
Why not?


270
00:22:27.310 --> 00:22:30.640
她是女傭而且是個黑人
She's a servant girl, and she has dark skin.


271
00:22:31.230 --> 00:22:32.390
那又怎么樣
So?


272
00:22:32.640 --> 00:22:35.810
這還不夠嗎
Well, doesn't that mean something?


273
00:23:20.690 --> 00:23:22.030
對不起  我不是
I'm sorry, I...


274
00:23:22.280 --> 00:23:24.530
需要我為你做什么  小姐
Is there anything I can do for you, miss?


275
00:23:24.780 --> 00:23:27.700
我只是上樓來換鞋
I just came up here to change my shoes.


276
00:23:28.480 --> 00:23:29.780
不  沒什么
No, there's nothing.


277
00:23:29.780 --> 00:23:34.870
請原諒  可你待在這里我們都會有麻煩
Well, then begging your pardon, but we'll both be in trouble if you stay.


278
00:23:40.630 --> 00:23:42.800
好了  姑娘們  排好隊
All right, girls, pair up.


279
00:23:44.970 --> 00:23:46.720
排好隊
Pair up.


280
00:24:17.660 --> 00:24:19.850
<b>親愛的貝琪  希望我們能成為朋友  莎拉</b>

281
00:24:38.440 --> 00:24:41.520
愛德華爵士看見女兒眼里的憂傷
"Sir Edward saw the sorrow in his daughter's eyes...


282
00:24:41.770 --> 00:24:44.940
但他知道家族榮譽是首要的
...but he knew that family honor must prevail at all costs.


283
00:24:45.190 --> 00:24:47.700
貴族身份不能被忽視
Nobility was not thought to be trifled with.


284
00:24:47.860 --> 00:24:50.620
"我向你求婚  夏洛特"  他說
'I beg of you, Charlotte,' he said.


285
00:24:50.780 --> 00:24:53.450
"答應約翰爵士春天嫁給他"
'Marry Sir John in the spring, as he has asked.'


286
00:24:53.700 --> 00:24:55.290
謝謝  拉維妮亞
Thank you, Lavinia.


287
00:24:55.540 --> 00:24:57.710
莎拉  你接著讀
Sara, you may take your turn.


288
00:25:09.380 --> 00:25:13.050
夏洛特轉過身對父親說  "父親  你是對的"
"Charlotte turned to her father and said, 'Father, you are right.


289
00:25:13.220 --> 00:25:16.810
"我必須打消那愚蠢瘋狂幼稚的想法"
'I must put away my foolish fancies and childhood wishes.'


290
00:25:27.320 --> 00:25:28.990
但我不想那么做
But I simply won't do it.


291
00:25:29.490 --> 00:25:30.740
對不起  父親
I'm sorry, Father.


292
00:25:30.990 --> 00:25:32.740
我不能嫁給我不愛的人
When I marry, it'll be for love.


293
00:25:33.160 --> 00:25:36.410
說著  夏洛特沖出房子
And with that, Charlotte ran from the house.


294
00:25:36.660 --> 00:25:39.500
在外面等待她的是英俊的馬夫  皮埃爾
Waiting outside was the handsome stable boy, Pierre...


295
00:25:39.750 --> 00:25:41.500
夏洛特心愛的王子
...whom Charlotte secretly adored.


296
00:25:41.920 --> 00:25:44.340
他們逃到海邊
Together they escaped to the coast


297
00:25:44.340 --> 00:25:46.750
坐船去塔帝島
and quickly set sail to the island for Tahiti.


298
00:25:47.000 --> 00:25:48.730
途中遭到
But when they were halfway there,


299
00:25:48.730 --> 00:25:51.760
一幫海盜的襲擊
their ship was attacked by band of pirates!


300
00:25:52.180 --> 00:25:54.260
不想被活著吃掉
Rather than be eaten alive...


301
00:25:54.510 --> 00:25:57.350
夏洛特和皮埃爾跳進洶涌的大海
...Charlotte and Pierre threw themselves into the raging sea.


302
00:25:57.520 --> 00:25:59.180
在他們將要被淹沒時
As they began to drown...


303
00:25:59.350 --> 00:26:03.440
緊緊擁抱著山盟海誓
...they held each other close, and swore undying love.


304
00:26:05.270 --> 00:26:09.530
絕望之際一群美人魚出現
But then, when all seemed lost, a group of mermaids appeared and rescued...


305
00:26:09.690 --> 00:26:10.860
別說了
Stop!


306
00:26:15.950 --> 00:26:17.370
你在干什么
What are you doing?


307
00:26:17.870 --> 00:26:20.630
我不忍心看她嫁給那個人
I couldn't bear to see Charlotte marry that man,


308
00:26:20.630 --> 00:26:22.540
就想像了另一個結局
so I imagined a different ending.


309
00:26:22.790 --> 00:26:23.870
你想像的
Imagined it?


310
00:26:25.290 --> 00:26:27.550
您從來不這樣嗎
Don't you ever do that, Miss Minchin?


311
00:26:27.880 --> 00:26:31.050
相信某種東西  讓它像是真的
Believe in something, just to make it seem real?


312
00:26:33.970 --> 00:26:36.890
什么都不缺的孩子才會想像
That's easy for a child who has everything.


313
00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:41.140
學校里不允許想像
There will be no more make-believe at this school...


314
00:26:41.390 --> 00:26:43.230
閱讀時間或其他時間都不允許
...during reading or any other time.


315
00:26:43.730 --> 00:26:46.560
-明白了嗎  -是  米切思小姐
-Is that understood?  -Yes, Miss Minchin.


316
00:26:46.980 --> 00:26:48.900
都回房間去
All of you, go to your bed this instant.


317
00:26:53.910 --> 00:26:56.740
我從沒聽過這么好聽的故事
I never heard a story like that in my whole life.


318
00:26:56.990 --> 00:27:00.750
你一定知道很多故事  對嗎  莎拉
I...I bet you know lots of them, don't you, Sara?


319
00:27:01.500 --> 00:27:03.920
不許說話
I want silence up there!


320
00:27:05.250 --> 00:27:08.920
我們得想法怎么對付這些規矩
We have to do something about this communication rule.


321
00:27:10.000 --> 00:27:12.260
等米切思小姐睡著后
Hey, after Minchin goes to bed...


322
00:27:12.510 --> 00:27:16.430
我們去你房間聽你給我們講故事
...we'll sneak into your room, and you can tell us a real story is.


323
00:27:16.680 --> 00:27:18.260
行嗎  莎拉
How about it, Sara?


324
00:27:18.510 --> 00:27:20.600
只能你們三個人來
Only if it's just you three.


325
00:27:43.540 --> 00:27:45.210
快來  快來
Come on, come on.


326
00:28:09.230 --> 00:28:13.230
怪獸拉瓦納把公主鎖在魔宮的塔樓上
The evil Ravana locked the princess up in his palace tower.


327
00:28:13.480 --> 00:28:15.650
好幾個星期
There she stayed for many weeks...


328
00:28:15.820 --> 00:28:18.320
公主看著窗外
...just staring out her window...


329
00:28:18.570 --> 00:28:20.990
非常思念她的王子
...missing her Prince Rama terribly.


330
00:28:39.840 --> 00:28:44.100
你真漂亮  就像愛米麗
Perfect. You look just like Emily.


331
00:28:45.600 --> 00:28:49.940
