Because he wants me to belong.


335
00:29:27.640 --> 00:29:32.730
我的小女兒  她會說法語  她真的會說法語
My little girl. She spoke French! She really spoke French.


336
00:29:35.230 --> 00:29:37.990
我和你母親為你自豪
Your mother and I are very proud of you.


337
00:29:45.910 --> 00:29:48.750
我抓到你了
I caught you, Nellie!


338
00:30:14.020 --> 00:30:15.440
爸爸
Papa!


339
00:31:05.070 --> 00:31:07.240
蘭道夫  喬思
Randolph... John!


340
00:31:11.410 --> 00:31:14.000
拉瑪王子向魔宮走去
Rama approached the thorny palace...


341
00:31:14.250 --> 00:31:16.920
他不知道怪獸拉瓦納正在等著他
