This is my room now, and I won't have you messing it up.


520
00:56:56.620 --> 00:56:59.250
這是什么味道真惡心
What is that awful smell?


521
00:56:59.250 --> 00:57:01.630
你上次洗澡是什么時候
When was your last time you had a bath?


522
00:57:09.300 --> 00:57:10.970
你在干什么
What are you doing?


523
00:57:11.390 --> 00:57:13.390
我不相信這一套
I don't believe in this!


524
00:57:13.980 --> 00:57:17.560
你快停下  停下
So you can just stop it! Stop it, I said!


525
00:57:22.400 --> 00:57:24.070
那是什么意思
What did you just do?


526
00:57:24.240 --> 00:57:27.070
幾句跟印度女巫學的咒話
Just a little curse I learned from a witch in India.


527
00:57:27.320 --> 00:57:28.570
咒語
Curse?


528
00:57:30.990 --> 00:57:33.660
-什么樣的咒語  -你會知道的
-What kind of curse?  -You'll see.


529
00:57:34.080 --> 00:57:37.830
不過我要是你就不那樣梳頭
But I wouldn't brush my hair as much if I were you.


530
00:57:50.090 --> 00:57:53.430
過來吧  這是我專門為你留的
It's all right. I saved it especially for you.


531
00:57:54.600 --> 00:57:56.520
來吧  吃吧
Go on. Take it.


532
00:58:23.290 --> 00:58:25.210
你就住在這里
Is this where you live?


533
00:58:25.460 --> 00:58:29.220
你不該來  這太冒險了
You shouldn't be here. It's too dangerous.


534
00:58:30.050 --> 00:58:34.140
為什么你不再喜歡我了  我做錯了什么嗎
Sara, why don't you like me anymore? Did I do something wrong?


535
00:58:34.390 --> 00:58:36.220
沒有  當然沒有
No, of course not.


536
00:58:36.470 --> 00:58:39.980
我以為你們不想再和我交朋友
I didn't think you'd want me for a friend...


537
00:58:40.650 --> 00:58:42.740
畢竟一切都變了
...now that things are different.


538
00:58:42.740 --> 00:58:47.400
我知道你沒有我這個朋友也很好
Sara, no, I'm sure you could do just fine without me for a friend...


539
00:58:47.650 --> 00:58:50.490
可我不能沒有你
...but I couldn't get along without you.


540
00:58:52.070 --> 00:58:53.660
對不起  我應該想到
I'm sorry. I should've known...


541
00:58:53.820 --> 00:58:56.490
你和別人不同
...you wouldn't be like the others.


542
00:58:56.740 --> 00:58:59.660
-什么聲音  -敲一聲表示"我在這里"
-What's that?  -One knock means "I'm here."


543
00:59:01.250 --> 00:59:03.830
敲兩聲表示"一切都好"
Two knocks means "All is well."


544
00:59:04.500 --> 00:59:07.090
敲三聲就是"沒有危險"
Three means "The coast is clear."


545
00:59:07.340 --> 00:59:09.370
"米切思女巫已經睡了"
'The demon Minchinweed is asleep.'


546
00:59:09.370 --> 00:59:12.010
這太刺激了
Gosh! It all sounds so adventurous!


547
00:59:12.260 --> 00:59:14.930
貝琪  來客人了
Look, Becky. We have a visitor.


548
00:59:15.430 --> 00:59:17.100
你好  貝琪
Hello, Becky.


549
00:59:18.020 --> 00:59:21.020
莎拉  我太想聽你講故事了
Oh, Sara, I miss your stories so much.


550
00:59:21.600 --> 00:59:25.610
告訴我們公主和王子后來怎樣了
Won't you tell us what happened to Rama and the princess?


551
00:59:25.860 --> 00:59:28.440
黃色的毒煙
The smoke from Ravana's arrows...


552
00:59:28.690 --> 00:59:31.030
終于散開
...finally began to lift.


553
00:59:31.860 --> 00:59:33.950
拉瑪倒在地上一動也不動
Rama lay dead on the ground.


554
00:59:34.700 --> 00:59:35.950
不
Oh, no!


555
00:59:36.200 --> 00:59:39.040
但是神奇的事發生了
But then a wonderful thing happened.


556
00:59:40.040 --> 00:59:44.960
一只羚羊來到王子身邊  用自己的生命救活了他
The gazelle laid down next to Rama, giving him his own life.


557
00:59:56.970 --> 00:59:59.310
他患有暫時性失憶癥
He's suffering from cute amnesia...


558
00:59:59.560 --> 01:00:02.560
是毒氣彈的副作用
...one of the rare side effects of poison gas.


559
01:00:02.810 --> 01:00:05.060
他的視力很快就會恢復
His eyes will heal in time.


560
01:00:05.310 --> 01:00:07.900
他的記憶就很難說了
His memory... who can say?


561
01:00:08.150 --> 01:00:09.730
他不是我兒子
He's not my son.


562
01:00:11.900 --> 01:00:14.070
很抱歉  蘭道夫先生
I'm sorry, Mr. Randolph.


563
01:00:14.910 --> 01:00:16.740
他被發現時身受重傷
He was found in severe shock...


564
01:00:16.990 --> 01:00:19.660
沒有軍服  沒有證件
...with no coat, no identification.


565
01:00:20.490 --> 01:00:23.500
因為只有您兒子還沒找到
Since your son was the only name unaccounted for...


566
01:00:23.750 --> 01:00:26.080
所以他們認為這是喬思
...they assumed this was John.


567
01:00:27.920 --> 01:00:29.500
很對不起
I am sorry.


568
01:00:39.010 --> 01:00:42.100
沒希望了  你認為我是個傻瓜
All the hoping. You must think me a fool.


569
01:00:43.180 --> 01:00:45.690
您希望自己是個聰明人  主人
Is it your wish to be wise, sahib?


570
01:00:46.020 --> 01:00:47.520
我不知道
I don't know.


571
01:00:48.520 --> 01:00:52.030
一個聰明人根本不會來這里
I suppose a wise man wouldn't have come here at all.


572
01:00:52.280 --> 01:00:53.610
聰明人
But if he had...


573
01:00:53.860 --> 01:00:57.370
會再仔細看看這位軍官
...he would have looked closely upon the soldier's face.


574
01:00:59.370 --> 01:01:00.950
能看出什么
What would he have seen?


575
01:01:01.200 --> 01:01:05.210
痛苦  先生  他需要照顧
Pain, sahib. He needs to be cared for.


576
01:01:06.790 --> 01:01:08.630
這不是我的責任
He's not my responsibility.


577
01:01:08.880 --> 01:01:13.130
聰明人記得他和喬思在一個軍團
A wise man would remember that this soldior was in John's regiment.


578
01:01:13.380 --> 01:01:18.470
如果他恢復記憶或許能告訴先生
If his memory returns, he might tell us what happened to his son.


579
01:01:20.550 --> 01:01:24.810
喬思正在英國某醫院里
Perhaps sahib will learn that John is in British hospital...


580
01:01:25.060 --> 01:01:30.230
等待著好心人幫他脫離痛苦  帶他回家
...wishing that a kind man would take him home, away from his pain.


581
01:01:34.990 --> 01:01:37.990
管道工來了  告訴他哪壞了
If the plumber comes, show him the problem.


582
01:01:38.240 --> 01:01:41.490
別和他聊天  他可是計時收費
And don't babble with this man. He's paid by the hour.


583
01:01:41.740 --> 01:01:45.080
我回來之前把拉丁文試卷判好
And make sure to correct the Latin tests by the time I get back.


584
01:01:45.330 --> 01:01:46.580
是  姐姐
Yes, sister.


585
01:01:52.090 --> 01:01:54.170
您好  米切思小姐
Hello, Miss Minchin.


586
01:01:55.590 --> 01:01:57.010
再見  米切思小姐
Goodbye, Miss Minchin.


587
01:02:24.700 --> 01:02:25.950
不  別這樣
Oh, no, not again!


588
01:02:31.380 --> 01:02:32.790
洛蒂  別這樣
Lottie, not again.


589
01:02:53.060 --> 01:02:54.820
快找那條項鍵
Let's find the locket.


590
01:02:56.650 --> 01:02:58.320
好了
All right...


591
01:02:59.320 --> 01:03:01.490
別鬧了
...it's okay. It's all right.


592
01:03:31.350 --> 01:03:33.520
我想洛蒂中邪了
Sara, come quick! It's Lottie, I think Lottie's possessed.


593
01:04:04.890 --> 01:04:05.890
找到了
I got it.


594
01:04:11.810 --> 01:04:14.730
你去管住那個小東西好嗎
Will you please get that child under control?


595
01:04:14.900 --> 01:04:16.900
別擔心  一切都好
Don't worry. Everything's fine.


596
01:04:47.260 --> 01:04:48.430
你怎么了
Well, what is it?


597
01:04:51.600 --> 01:04:53.430
我想我看見了老鼠
I thought I saw a mouse.


598
01:05:13.370 --> 01:05:14.870
你好
Hello.


599
01:05:23.470 --> 01:05:26.800
那孩子是撤旦派來折磨我的
I swear, that child has a pact with Satan to destroy me.


600
01:05:27.050 --> 01:05:29.800
這工作不適合我  我沒有耐心
I'm not cut out for this job. I have no patience for children.


601
01:05:30.050 --> 01:05:33.140
教書要記住那么多可怕的東西
And teaching! All those horrible facts to remember.


602
01:05:33.390 --> 01:05:34.980
我簡直煩透了
I don't like it at all.


603
01:05:35.230 --> 01:05:37.650
你喜歡法蘭西斯  是嗎
You like Frances, don't you?


604
01:05:37.900 --> 01:05:38.980
什么
What?


605
01:05:39.480 --> 01:05:42.320
當然不是  你怎么敢這么說
Of course not. How dare you.


606
01:05:42.480 --> 01:05:43.990
我想他也喜歡你
I think he likes you too.


607
01:05:45.820 --> 01:05:47.240
是嗎
You do?


608
01:05:48.320 --> 01:05:49.320
真的
Really?


609
01:05:49.490 --> 01:05:52.490
你們應該遠走高飛去結婚
I think you should run away and get married.


610
01:05:52.660 --> 01:05:55.000
這該有多浪漫
It'd be terribly romantic.


611
01:05:55.830 --> 01:05:58.330
多么令人激動
What an extraordinary thing to say.


612
01:06:07.430 --> 01:06:12.100
可是我姐姐知道了會大發雷雷
Well, anyway, my sister would be furious if she found out.


613
01:06:12.100 --> 01:06:15.020
那時你早走遠了
So, you'd be long gone by then.


614
01:06:15.350 --> 01:06:17.850
和勇敢的法蘭西斯一起
Living in some exotic paradise...


615
01:06:18.100 --> 01:06:21.020
生活在你們的伊甸園里
...with that dashing young milkman.


616
01:06:23.520 --> 01:06:26.190
我得去集市了
I'd better get to the market.


617
01:06:47.300 --> 01:06:49.380
你做得很好  年輕人
You're doing well, young man.


618
01:06:49.720 --> 01:06:51.390
你馬上就到家了
You're almost home.


619
01:06:53.640 --> 01:06:56.640
請相信我的眼睛  主人
You must trust my eyes, sahib.


620
01:07:24.840 --> 01:07:26.250
怎么回事
What's going on?


621
01:07:26.500 --> 01:07:27.760
一個驚喜
It's a surprise.


622
01:07:32.590 --> 01:07:35.850
-你們怎么來了  -我們給你帶來樣東西
-What are you doing here?  - We brought you something.


623
01:07:40.430 --> 01:07:44.110
莎拉公主  我們為你找回了一件東西
Princess Sara, we like to present you with something we rescued.


624
01:07:44.770 --> 01:07:46.440
歷經驚心動魄的歷險
In a dangerous adventure.


625
01:07:46.690 --> 01:07:49.780
-我們自己的軍事行動  -冒著生命危險
-Our very own crusade.  -Risking all our lives.


626
01:07:49.940 --> 01:07:51.450
還有我
And mine too.


627
01:07:59.950 --> 01:08:02.210
我不知道該說什么
I don't know what to say.


628
01:08:05.130 --> 01:08:09.050
你們是我最好的朋友
You are the best friends anyone could ever ask for.


629
01:08:13.000 --> 01:08:16.970
沒事的  這是我的小朋友  漢納曼
It's all right. It's just my little monkey friend, Hanuman.


630
01:08:17.970 --> 01:08:20.470
他是從哪來的
Where did he come from?


631
01:08:20.890 --> 01:08:22.730
就是隔壁  看
Right next door. Look.


632
01:08:24.030 --> 01:08:25.980
漢納曼喜歡來做客
Hanuman likes to come to visit me all the time.


633
01:08:26.480 --> 01:08:28.650
你能和他說話嗎
Can you really talk to him, Sara?


634
01:08:28.650 --> 01:08:29.650
當然
Sure!


635
01:08:29.900 --> 01:08:33.240
漢納曼  跟我的朋友們打個招呼
Hanuman, say hello to all my friends.


636
01:08:54.430 --> 01:08:57.120
拉瑪醒來后
After Rama came back to life...


637
01:08:57.120 --> 01:09:01.600
跑到怪獸的魔宮去救公主
...he raced towards the monster's palace to rescue Sita.


638
01:09:01.930 --> 01:09:02.850
可是突然
Suddenly...


639
01:09:03.350 --> 01:09:05.350
拉瓦納出現了
...Ravana appeared!


640
01:09:20.120 --> 01:09:23.370
我們還是以后再接著講吧
I think we better save the rest of the story for later.


641
01:09:41.220 --> 01:09:42.970
你們在這里干什么
What's going on here?


642
01:09:43.390 --> 01:09:45.890
不是她們的錯  是我叫她們來的
It's not their fault. I asked them to come.


643
01:09:46.140 --> 01:09:47.730
你們五個立即下樓
You five go downstairs immediately.


644
01:09:47.900 --> 01:09:49.480
以后再處理
I'll deal with you later.


645
01:09:50.980 --> 01:09:51.820
貝琪
Becky...


646
01:09:52.400 --> 01:09:55.020
你明天關在自己的屋里
...you'll remain locked in your room for the entire day tomorrow


647
01:09:55.020 --> 01:09:56.070
別想吃飯
without meals.


648
01:09:56.320 --> 01:09:57.320
快走
Go!


649
01:10:00.240 --> 01:10:04.000
她的活也歸你干
And you will perform all her chores in addition to your own...


650
01:10:04.250 --> 01:10:06.750
并且沒有早餐  午餐和晚餐
...without breakfast, lunch or dinner.


651
01:10:07.000 --> 01:10:08.500
你應該明白
It's time you learned, Sara Crewe...


652
01:10:08.750 --> 01:10:12.590
現實生活不是你幻想的故事
...that real life has nothing to do with your fantasy games.


653
01:10:12.840 --> 01:10:15.420
這是個殘酷骯臟的世界
It's a cruel, nasty world out there...


654
01:10:15.670 --> 01:10:18.430
我們的責任就是盡量做到最好
...and it's our duty to make the best of it.


655
01:10:18.680 --> 01:10:23.760
不要沉浸在愚蠢的幻想中  而是讓自己成為有用的人
Not to indulge in ridiculous dreams, but to be productive and useful.


656
01:10:27.180 --> 01:10:29.940
聽明白我的話了嗎
Do you understand what I'm saying?


657
01:10:32.610 --> 01:10:34.030
是的  女士
Yes, ma'am.


658
01:10:36.440 --> 01:10:37.610
很好
Good.


659
01:10:40.200 --> 01:10:42.950
可我并不相信
But I don't believe in it.


660
01:10:46.040 --> 01:10:49.120
別跟我說你仍舊是什么公主
Don't tell me you still fancy yourself a princess.


661
01:10:50.120 --> 01:10:52.630
上帝  看看你周圍
Good God, child, look around you!


662
01:10:53.130 --> 01:10:55.800
去照照鏡子
Or better yet, look in the mirror.


663
01:11:03.470 --> 01:11:05.140
我是公主
I am a princess.


664
01:11:05.390 --> 01:11:06.970
所有的女孩都是
All girls are.


665
01:11:07.310 --> 01:11:10.060
即使她們住在窄小的閣樓上
Even if they live in tiny old attics.


666
01:11:10.390 --> 01:11:12.650
即使她們穿得破破爛爛
Even if they dress in rags.


667
01:11:13.560 --> 01:11:16.980
即使她們不漂亮不聰明不再年輕
Even if they aren't pretty or smart or young.


668
01:11:17.440 --> 01:11:21.110
她們還是公主  我們全都是
They're still princesses. All of us.


669
01:11:22.320 --> 01:11:24.910
您父親沒有告訴過你
Didn't your father ever tell you that?


670
01:11:25.660 --> 01:11:26.870
他沒有嗎
Didn't he?


671
01:11:31.170 --> 01:11:33.670
我再發現你和別的女孩在這里
If I find you up here with any other girls again...


672
01:11:33.920 --> 01:11:36.500
就把你扔到街上去
...I'll throw you out into the street!


673
01:12:10.040 --> 01:12:11.660
我們該怎么辦
What're we going to do?


674
01:12:13.040 --> 01:12:15.420
整天都會沒有飯吃
A whole day with nothing to eat.


675
01:12:15.960 --> 01:12:17.710
貝琪  別哭
Don't cry, Becky.


676
01:12:18.050 --> 01:12:19.710
我很害伯
I'm scared.


677
01:12:19.960 --> 01:12:23.470
如果米切思把我趕走  我沒有地方可去
If Minchin throws me out, I've got no place to go.


678
01:12:24.720 --> 01:12:26.220
放心吧
That's not true.


679
01:12:26.720 --> 01:12:31.310
我會陪著你  我一直覺得我們是姐妹
I'm here with you. I've always thought of us as sisters.


680
01:12:32.060 --> 01:12:33.310
是真的
You have?


681
01:12:33.560 --> 01:12:37.060
我們發誓永遠照顧對方
Let's make a promise riight now to always look out for each other.


682
01:12:37.400 --> 01:12:38.480
我發誓
It's a promise.


683
01:12:41.440 --> 01:12:44.570
現在怎么能找點吃的呢
Now, what are we going to do about food?


684
01:12:45.410 --> 01:12:47.160
我們會餓死的
Starve, I guess.


685
01:12:47.410 --> 01:12:50.580
不會  我們要做一件事
No, there's only one thing to do.


686
01:12:50.830 --> 01:12:53.920
睡覺前吃一頓豐盛的晚宴
We'll eat a great feast before we go to sleep...


687
01:12:54.170 --> 01:12:56.420
這樣明天就不會覺得餓
...and that will keep us full all day tomorrow.


688
01:12:56.670 --> 01:12:59.500
晚宴  什么晚宴
Feast? What feast?


689
01:12:59.710 --> 01:13:01.590
你看
Just look around.


690
01:13:02.800 --> 01:13:04.590
看見那邊的桌子了嗎
Do you see that table there?


691
01:13:05.260 --> 01:13:07.470
鋪著潔白的臺布
It's covered with a beautiful cloth...


692
01:13:07.680 --> 01:13:08.930
還有蠟燭
...and candles...


693
01:13:09.260 --> 01:13:12.020
托盤里放著各種美味可口的食物
